{"type":null,"faqId":35640,"title":"为什么闪光灯只有一个亮/下面的闪光灯不亮？","answer":"手电筒模式下只会亮一个灯（也就是camera界面灯泡的那个图标），除了camera界面的灯泡图标,其余(闪电图标,闪电+A图标)都是亮2个灯，拍照时闪三次，第一次对焦闪只亮白灯，第二次预闪只亮白灯，最后一次强闪一般是两颗灯同时亮，如果说一直一颗灯亮,那么可以确认下是不是一颗灯坏了。\n\n确认方法:可以在打开闪电图标的情况下,在全黑环境对着白墙拍照会出现偏色。\n\n用手指捂住闪光灯是看不出有几颗灯亮的，简单检测方法就是用一张纸盖住闪光灯测试。","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"420","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437124657000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":141,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀7,honor7,PLK,Plank,闪光灯","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}